<body>
    <h1>T6 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"449d8f58b806" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f21c619faa9e" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"aa59c87c3156">The purpose of this document is to describe th=
e technical implementation of deploying two static frontend applications on=
 an Apache web server using subdomains and securing them with Let=E2=80=99s=
 Encrypt SSL certificates.</p>
<p local-id=3D"698e8fb77555">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e6592fdd0d83">
<li local-id=3D"def09d682fe3">
<p local-id=3D"7b0d1fdd0512">CTO =E2=80=93 To review deployment architectur=
e and security posture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0bfda7665a09">
<p local-id=3D"13a3cf7c05f8">Developers =E2=80=93 To understand hosting and=
 configuration setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bd54254f0eff">
<p local-id=3D"5a1f8a7b1605">Solution Architects =E2=80=93 To review infras=
tructure design</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d56e9ad9c31">
<p local-id=3D"47e45fb0f681">DevOps Engineers =E2=80=93 To validate deploym=
ent and security process</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6975803b15fc">
<p local-id=3D"5a406df5e958">Resellers / Stakeholders =E2=80=93 To understa=
nd hosting setup and compliance</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c943ad828d3c">
<h2 local-id=3D"a84a81b30995" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"94180ad247b3">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6de5460392e9">
<li local-id=3D"1dea5617e6c4">
<p local-id=3D"bcd563ee5157">Apache installation and configuration on Ubunt=
u server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8375ac609283">
<p local-id=3D"3df964590667">Deployment of two static frontend applications=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef1e9c7e85fc">
<p local-id=3D"7f0163a7eab1">Subdomain-based hosting using Virtual Hosts</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"60f37a25a405">
<p local-id=3D"3449bf4864ec">DNS configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5e0eb072493">
<p local-id=3D"4da8abba9fe3">SSL certificate implementation using Let=E2=80=
=99s Encrypt</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"885a24cebb51">
<p local-id=3D"d48a54b5f3c5">HTTPS enforcement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5e28afc8a4e">
<p local-id=3D"6de1870f788e">Auto-renewal verification</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b6c283e1b0a8">This document does not cover CI/CD pipelines, =
containerization, load balancing, or monitoring systems, as they were not p=
art of the assigned task.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e96609766d5c">
<h1 local-id=3D"c21a1b941946" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"01d70d3e36bd" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b8dbec7fde8b">This DevOps project involved deploying two sta=
tic frontend applications on a Linux-based Apache server using subdomains a=
nd securing them with SSL.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5ef172383451">Benefits achieved:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c96b11df1764">
<li local-id=3D"4bb1b9a60999">
<p local-id=3D"19d69ce84a72">Structured multi-application hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94ff87f98299">
<p local-id=3D"0997b95faef9">Secure HTTPS communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c63b4a3509f3">
<p local-id=3D"6121619308df">Proper domain mapping</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbd5e85ffbd2">
<p local-id=3D"bb506ebb55e5">Automated certificate renewal</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6f550a3ed45c">
<h2 local-id=3D"92494b3b4b40" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrinciples(A=
WSWell-ArchitectedFramework)">2.2 Key Principles (AWS Well-Architected Fram=
ework)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4d454fdcfeb9">This implementation aligns with the AWS Well-A=
rchitected Framework pillars:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a03c25d089f5" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-1.OperationalExcel=
lence">1. Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3cf5e5f3f88d">
<li local-id=3D"59cc531cd158">
<p local-id=3D"89650e288173">Structured configuration using Virtual Hosts</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"889ca1cbc0dd">
<p local-id=3D"ad0fdf273878">Clear directory separation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11728924d802">
<p local-id=3D"25d5e3c631f1">Apache configuration validation using <code>ap=
achectl configtest</code></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b10279a3f12a" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.Security">2. Sec=
urity</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"33f9050f7a65">
<li local-id=3D"3bc7eb3cc2e9">
<p local-id=3D"5498eeaccb24">HTTPS enabled via Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"1dd4933b69c8">
<p local-id=3D"2863a3ddc4f0">TLS encryption implemented</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c2cc2c78155">
<p local-id=3D"e9bef6e7e506">HTTP =E2=86=92 HTTPS redirection enabled</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e91f1a803122">
<p local-id=3D"d6926c4c68d8">Proper file ownership (<code>www-data</code>) =
enforced</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"634c884b59a8">
<p local-id=3D"8798d2cc9088">Security group restricted to required ports (2=
2, 80, 443)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"05786d15abe9" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-3.Reliability">3. =
Reliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"db18ff5a6add">
<li local-id=3D"ec5fdd6ccff0">
<p local-id=3D"459ca496a73e">DNS-based routing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03df25b9787e">
<p local-id=3D"7333e147109a">SSL auto-renewal validation using dry-run</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"01311d29e899">
<p local-id=3D"a837ce7b52f3">Apache service reload without downtime</p></li=
>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f1f95c3ae7a3" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-4.PerformanceEffic=
iency">4. Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"fd11a0e3a5cf">
<li local-id=3D"0b983b7590b5">
<p local-id=3D"9f9a5d7a661b">Static applications served directly via Apache=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d010cd6ec413">
<p local-id=3D"813808bb6fb9">No backend processing overhead</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"9e603a304080" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-5.CostOptimization=
">5. Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f66abff39b83">
<li local-id=3D"e42525c4e42d">
<p local-id=3D"022f8dc68f59">Ubuntu EC2 instance (minimal size)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"950e40d0c182">
<p local-id=3D"40925208f60e">Free SSL via Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fe72dd578ee">
<p local-id=3D"34e7d8b293df">No paid load balancer or external services</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8f5fa026153c" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-6.Sustainability">=
6. Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"b7a0b19b0d10">
<li local-id=3D"5b3f38e3c547">
<p local-id=3D"98a4118f1869">Minimal infrastructure usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d251c5d96a9">
<p local-id=3D"1854cb474bd6">Single-instance static hosting</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"58cabfe301af">
<h2 local-id=3D"fa855d07cf5a" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"92581b48ff52">The primary objectives were:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4cff1ffe6f8d">
<li local-id=3D"8a728a6bdea3">
<p local-id=3D"85e0af2fe19f">Deploy two frontend applications from the prov=
ided repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e626c58b53a">
<p local-id=3D"da0f31b5652f">Host them using personalized subdomains</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"11dce32094e9">
<p local-id=3D"6d4f00b06746">Configure Apache Virtual Hosts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1644187f77d">
<p local-id=3D"06041bfe21bc">Enable HTTPS for both applications</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d00d0087433">
<p local-id=3D"d8f15c4177ac">Ensure automatic SSL renewal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b77430027ba2">
<p local-id=3D"9db77f0d5060">Validate secure browser access</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"cec6ad925cd2">
<h2 local-id=3D"b3299caf0d9f" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"17b19e8a8f8a" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">Const=
raints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"475ea759f679">
<li local-id=3D"5348f34ed4fd">
<p local-id=3D"ebe6447c6ead">Single Ubuntu EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f7d5ba33350">
<p local-id=3D"307b61455951">Time limit: 6 hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11ef0ac5b106">
<p local-id=3D"4e22b5aa1bfe">Static applications only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fd1d6a79451">
<p local-id=3D"eb34ff328c8f">No CI/CD tools allowed</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"811570691642" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">Assum=
ptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"91e2a1fa2e7d">
<li local-id=3D"bba0bcb4af75">
<p local-id=3D"bca242483659">Domain already purchased and managed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d77f4fdaacd3">
<p local-id=3D"1b3b322b3b31">DNS records configurable</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"876c8d1a6c02">
<p local-id=3D"e64e7a84608b">Ports 80 and 443 accessible</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"76321e94feb2">
<h1 local-id=3D"6dc0f6a46d32" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"35be8f3e5484" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ed633223280a">The infrastructure consisted of:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"73c2ddec4bec">
<li local-id=3D"5c1ec9f3c2c2">
<p local-id=3D"4a9485e3c518">AWS EC2 Ubuntu Server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e6608bf3080">
<p local-id=3D"3ae0c26c8344">Public IP address</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb7c2abd8e99">
<p local-id=3D"668e10723c64">Domain: pushkar.cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"402250825038">
<p local-id=3D"b26be43ff7a1">Apache Web Server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ea6fcf29355">
<p local-id=3D"54592bdc7417">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt Certbot</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"75a1f7460055" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-ArchitectureDiagra=
m">Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ffb77c2ac605">Traffic Flow:</p>
<p local-id=3D"6f5e38953ac1">User =E2=86=92 DNS =E2=86=92 EC2 Public IP =E2=
=86=92 Apache =E2=86=92 Virtual Host =E2=86=92 Application Directory</p><sp=
an class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluenc=
e-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-cente=
r" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-10-2026-10_54_04-PM-20260310-173242.png" width=
