<hr local-id=3D"975c36da2285">
<h2 local-id=3D"4e060fa4483e" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environments">3=
.2 Environments</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5e039ed6f6b6">Only one environment was used:</p>
<p local-id=3D"cdc4a51f8737">Production Environment</p>
<p local-id=3D"0f955050d120">Since this was a deployment task, no separate =
staging or development environments were implemented.</p>
