<hr local-id=3D"c7dc3e521469">
<h2 local-id=3D"4f6b6f7b2f26" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-3.4ApplicationArch=
itecture&amp;UserRequestFlow">3.4 Application Architecture &amp; User Reque=
st Flow</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"2413091b8fd7" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-ArchitectureFlow">=
Architecture Flow</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"7f379a9125fd">
<li local-id=3D"76c52a5db4c7">
<p local-id=3D"6923c6cb3ab8">User enters subdomain</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71d7b95d442d">
<p local-id=3D"9261a41be6f3">DNS resolves to EC2 public IP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4dab456a3609">
<p local-id=3D"de1dfaf3214a">Apache listens on port 80/443</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"016c4e4e76a6">
<p local-id=3D"11b7bbc9171d">Virtual Host matches ServerName</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2deddfa34463">
<p local-id=3D"91715b5ad024">Apache serves content from respective director=
y</p></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"70a6848b46d7" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-SecuredRequestFlow=
(HTTPS)">Secured Request Flow (HTTPS)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ff98871d2244">User =E2=86=92 HTTPS Request =E2=86=92 Port 44=
3 =E2=86=92 Apache =E2=86=92 SSL Certificate Validation =E2=86=92 Encrypted=
 Response</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ad5a006d407a">
<h1 local-id=3D"76aee939e18d" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentPract=
ices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<p local-id=3D"7faac7e292c5">Since the applications were static frontend ap=
plications, no development or CI/CD processes were implemented.</p>
<p local-id=3D"34d3736f026c">The repository was cloned directly from GitHub=
 and deployed without modification.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"24d05bff96a5">
<h1 local-id=3D"6e3c10330dc4" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-5.DeploymentandRel=
easeManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"696e68c44344" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentStrat=
egy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a169aa898253">Manual deployment strategy was used:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"44a5273ff067">
<li local-id=3D"e7e239b19c01">
<p local-id=3D"0d7119d640dc">Clone repository</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d21067be216b">
<p local-id=3D"2846274ae8fb">Create application directories</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e451b49b613d">
<p local-id=3D"5e79f17131aa">Copy static files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6002faa6c3c">
<p local-id=3D"35779aea9471">Configure Virtual Hosts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38eaa930fa13">
<p local-id=3D"fe3e681571b1">Reload Apache</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ad041c9c0eb8">This ensured clean separation between applicat=
ions.</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapp=
