<hr local-id=3D"ca010b149c6f">
<h2 local-id=3D"0d27cc421e14" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-5.2ConfigurationMa=
nagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a0c7d896728f">Configuration was handled using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f215329c861a">
<li local-id=3D"bfddbbf9e8d6">
