<hr local-id=3D"b077b777892f">
<h2 local-id=3D"3ad3f4931844" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousDeliv=
ery">5.3 Continuous Delivery</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5be28d33efc5">Not applicable.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba13e8bda996">Deployment was manual as per assignment scope.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b97e13435e43">
<h1 local-id=3D"96cc1b07e510" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-6.MonitoringandInc=
identManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e692520b7884">No external monitoring tools were configured a=
s it was not part of the assignment.</p>
<p local-id=3D"eade39371038">Basic validation performed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a65ee386e8a8">
<li local-id=3D"f409ba923534">
<p local-id=3D"6084a66761b4">Apache service status check</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5be09cb1c0d5">
<p local-id=3D"cffcbebe9dfd">DNS resolution validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed71f4bc9b12">
<p local-id=3D"0096157e9df1">SSL certificate verification</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6ec103901b3">
<p local-id=3D"3a1542a5037d">Renewal dry-run test</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
