<hr local-id=3D"a9a53f02506c">
<h1 local-id=3D"d937275f3826" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Com=
pliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"372695791e6a">Security best practices implemented:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"959b9e6d27ea">
<li local-id=3D"1d59ac6fcc53">
<p local-id=3D"d503c3a79c2f">HTTPS via Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f0fedc287b7">
<p local-id=3D"e551ca5171da">TLS encryption enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bee56719eda9">
<p local-id=3D"3dd8949dbe10">HTTP automatically redirected to HTTPS</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"030b58441fbf">
<p local-id=3D"f3edf4b95480">Apache running under restricted user (<code>ww=
w-data</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afbaad41bd9c">
<p local-id=3D"021d08c9cc80">Proper file permissions (755)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0af9aa0ea0be">
<p local-id=3D"bd032022fcf6">AWS Security Group restricted to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"069f8c6dc4dd">
<li local-id=3D"16d818dd7ba2">
<p local-id=3D"3ba02598d20a">22 (SSH)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"feb326a6698a">
<p local-id=3D"eca0b92364c6">80 (HTTP)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c70161c0376d">
<p local-id=3D"dc23e3c56e93">443 (HTTPS)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e94e26bc507e">No unnecessary ports exposed.</p><span class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedd=
ed-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=
