<h2 local-id=3D"88ab2739443e" id=3D"T6-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">12.1 =
Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0415d877c044">Two frontend applications were successfully de=
ployed on an Apache web server using personalized subdomains and secured us=
ing Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt SSL certificates.</p>
<p local-id=3D"dec17fea0d53">The deployment ensures:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"86b025e0d4ba">
<li local-id=3D"561cbe1361b1">
<p local-id=3D"62b38cd2f1ca">Secure HTTPS communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3204c405d030">
<p local-id=3D"fbc5371ee2de">Proper domain mapping</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed04ef9f8666">
<p local-id=3D"09f9358582e6">Clean Apache configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b140c025488">
<p local-id=3D"38f9ad7d3c03">Automatic certificate renewal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5697975be159">
<p local-id=3D"79dfc24ffc18">AWS security compliance</p></li>
</ul>
